998	// ---- Round 6: --diff summary line taxonomy (RHS / LHS / DiffLemma) -------------
999	//
1000	// Under `--diff` the summary body gains prefixed line forms (captures r6_diff_*):
1001	//   `  RHS :  <name> (<kind>): <verdict> (<N> steps)`   projected ordinary lemma
1002	//   `  LHS :  <name> (<kind>): <verdict> (<N> steps)`   projected ordinary lemma
1003	//   `  DiffLemma:  <name> : <verdict> (<N> steps)`      observational equivalence
1004	// The verdict phrases are the same set as non-diff lemmas; a DiffLemma has no
1005	// trace-kind and its `falsified` always reads `- found trace`.
